text: Lynn County is a county in the U.S. state of Texas. In 2020, 5,596 people lived there. The county seat is Tahoka. == History == The county was created in 1876. == Geography == The county has a total area of 893 square miles. == References == Category:Texas counties Category:1876 establishments in the United States Category:1870s establishments in Texas
title: Lynn County, Texas
